step.action:
Modify ClassificationParser in services/policy_agent/src/gpu_inference.py:

1. Add class-level regex:
   _THINK_BLOCK_RE: re.Pattern[str] = re.compile(
       r"<think>.*?</think>", re.DOTALL | re.IGNORECASE,
   )

2. Replace parse() method body:
   @classmethod
   def parse(cls, text: str) -> str:
       if not text:
           return "DENY"
       # Canonicalize: strip think blocks (Faramesh principle)
       cleaned = cls._THINK_BLOCK_RE.sub("", text).strip()
       target = cleaned if cleaned else text
       # Zero-trust: require exactly one label
       matches = cls._LABEL_PATTERN.findall(target)
       if len(matches) != 1:
           return "DENY"  # Ambiguous, adversarial, or unparseable → fail-closed
       return matches[0].upper()
